{
  "stem": "2533.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if we had a little bit of changing of clothes, to put it all under, so but it won't be suspected that we are a little bit bigger, because we were going, and the [?fourties?] of October was late autumn in-- in Europe, in Poland.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we had-- and I still had my coat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I looked after it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't wear it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I used to have it under my head, that was almost like a pillow to sleep on it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I- I had my coat that day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I took it with me, even if it was not so cold, but I had it on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I had a scarf.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I had a little-- a little bag and a few cubes of sugar that German gave me-- I put into that bag.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And by while I was running-- and yeah, something happened to that bag.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But when we were going to march out the main gate, because going out any other way, the wires had to be cut, and they were-- there were current in it.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the mines had to be detonated because there were three fences.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "In between the second and the third fence, there were mines.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So and to run to the forest, something had to be done before we could run there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not straight away.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when somebody ask about them, they just went somewhere and all that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But Frenzel was going in, too, and he changed his mind.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he came out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he discovered-- and Bauer, another scharfuhrer, came from the third camp with a truck.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And something had to be unloaded.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'm not so sure what it was there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they couldn't find somebody because it was nearly roll call and finish of work.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
